OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome bright
OL,6,Fspells in the early evening, although
OL,7,Fscattered showers remain possible.
OL,8,FTurning cloudy overnight with rain and
OL,9,Fshowers, this heavy at times,
OL,10,Fspreading east. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy to start, gradually
OL,13,Fturning brighter from the west as rain
OL,14,Fclears away eastwards. A chance of
OL,15,Fshowers for a time in the afternoon.
OL,16,FWinds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
