OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,6,Fwinds Sunday, with rain spreading
OL,7,Feast. Breezy Monday with bright spells
OL,8,Fbut mostly dry. Light rain Tuesday may
OL,9,Fclear later, but mostly cloudy.
OL,10,FBreezy. Temperatures a little above
OL,11,Faverage.
